In this case, the compound consists of carbon, hydrogen, and oxygen atoms. The structural formula indicates there are 7 carbon atoms, 8 hydrogen atoms, and 3 oxygen atoms present in the compound.

Therefore, the molecular formula of 4-methyl-1,3-dioxolan-2-one; prop-1-ene can be determined as C7H8O3.
